---
title: Chicken Schnitzel & Cheddar Potatoes with Onion Gravy & Avocado Salad
description: There you have it, a chicken schnitzel and roast potato feast, but there’s a surprise hidden in here, ready to entertain you with
dazzling flavours. It’s all in the Cheddar melted over the potatoes and a caramelised onion sauce for the chicken. Sorry for spoiling
the surprise but we couldn’t contain our excitement!

